<eesti>OTE on kohustatud LRAIC s&uuml;steemi rakendamiseks kasutama &uuml;lalt-alla l&auml;henemist 1. jaanuarist 2001. a.&Uuml;lalt-alla l&auml;henemise p&otilde;him&otilde;tted lisaks &uuml;ldistele n&otilde;uetele on toodud k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses. </eesti>
<inglise>An undertaking with significant market power shall use the top-down approach for implementing LRAIC as of 1 January 2001.The principles of the top-down approach together with the general requirements are set out in this Regulation. </inglise>
