<inglise>Economy of scale as an important factor in describing average and incremental costs </inglise>
<eesti>Praktikas arvutatakse kogu teenuse lisanduv kulu &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu operaatori jaoks, arvestades v&auml;lditavaid kulusid, kui seda teenust poleks osutatud. </eesti>
<inglise>In practice the incremental cost of the total service is calculated for the public telecommunications network operator so that costs avoided if such service were not provided are taken into account. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui defineerida juurdekasvu kogu teenusele, siis kogu teenuse lisanduvad kulud erinevad traditsioonilisest keskmisest piirkulust lisanduvate teenuse-spetsiifiliste fikseeritud kulude v&otilde;rra (vt lisa 2). </eesti>
<inglise>When defining the increment to total service, the incremental costs of the total service differ from the traditional average marginal cost by service specific fixed costs which are added thereto (see Annex 2). </inglise>
