<inglise>Incremental costs based on network components </inglise>
<eesti>Mingi tegevuse PSTN opereerimisega mitteseotud tegevuste kulud ongi vaheks selle tegevuse kogukulude ja PSTN opereerimisega seotud eraldiseisvate kulude vahel. </eesti>
<inglise>The cost of activities not related to the operation of PSTN of an activity is the difference between total cost of the activity and separate costs related to the operation of PSTN. </inglise>
<eesti>Antud juhul saab selle arvutada, korrutades PSTN opereerimisega mitteseotud teenuse mahu (500) kulude ja mahu seosega 0,8 (joonisel &agr;, mis matemaatiliselt vordub arctan 0,8). </eesti>
<inglise>Here, it can be calculated by multiplying the volume of activities not related to the operation of PSTN (500) with the cost-volume coefficient 0,8 (&mgr; in the Figure, equals to arctan 0,8). </inglise>
<eesti>Need PSTN opereerimisega mitteseotud tegevuse lisanduvad kulud on 400 (kuna 100 ehk 20% on &oacgr;ldkulude osa). </eesti>
<inglise>This incremental cost of an activity not related to the operation of PSTN is 400 (since 100 or 20% is part of the overhead costs). </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lekandev&otilde;rgu opereerimisega seotud tegevuse lisanduvad kulud saab arvutada, vaadates l&auml;bi erinevuse mingi tegevuse X kogukulude ja sama teenuse osutamise vahel. </eesti>
<inglise>The incremental cost of an activity not related to the operation of a transmission network can be calculated by examining the difference between the total cost of activity X and the provision of the same service. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui on lineaarne kulude ja mahu vaheline seos, saab selle arvutada kui 400&times;0, 8 = 320 (sellest 20% on &uuml;ldkulud). </eesti>
<inglise>If the cost-volume relationship is linear, it can be calculated 400&times;0.8 = 320 (whereas 20% is overhead costs). </inglise>
<eesti>Juurdep&auml;&auml;suv&otilde;rguga seotud lisanduva kulu saab arvutada analoogiliselt 100&times;0, 8=80. </eesti>
<inglise>The incremental cost of an access network can be calculated in a similar manner 100&times;0.8 = 80. </inglise>
<eesti>Nende eespool nimetatud lisanduvate kulude summa kokku on 800, mis on 200 v&otilde;rra v&auml;hem antud tegevuse kogukuludest. </eesti>
<inglise>The sum of those incremental costs specified above is 800 which is 200 less than the total cost of the activity. </inglise>
<eesti>See vahe (200) on tegevuse &uuml;ldkulud. </eesti>
<inglise>This difference (200) is the overhead costs of the activity. </inglise>
